[13.142777, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “Same hash, in a browser. This is the AI Bill of Materials on glaas.ai —”\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;33m  “CycloneDX, downloadable, every input with its content hash.”\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;32m$ open https://glaas.ai — paste the hash, click Audit (AI-BOM)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  [NET] fallback: cast/glaas-aibom.cast\u001b[0m\r\n"]
